&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you don&amp;rsquo;t have &lt;code&gt;deep_sleep&lt;/code&gt; block, the imports are going to be missing in the CPP code, hence you can&amp;rsquo;t use ESP_GPIO_WAKEUP_GPIO_HIGH, etc, in the CPP code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
